To declare a string value we can use " " with words and numbers to turn it into string
- Example:
local string = "This Is String"
print(string)
===> Output: This Is String


- You can link string with string, string with number, number with number using ..
* Note: when using .. , your data type will become string
- Example:
local x = "This".." Is".." String"
print(x)
===> Output: This Is String

local x = 11 ..22
print(type(x),x)
===> Output: string  1122
